msgid ""
"When you select an action, that opens a sub-window where you can choose "
"between two radio buttons, <guilabel>Default</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Custom</guilabel>. If you choose <guilabel>Default</guilabel> "
"you'll use the default shortcut. If you choose <guilabel>Custom</guilabel> "
"you'll configure and use your shortcut for this action."
